# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist-ssr
*.local

# NOTE: `dist/` is deliberately NOT ignored — it is the deployed site.
# GitHub Pages serves pre-built files; it does not run our build. So the built
# output is committed on purpose. Rebuild with `npm run build` before pushing, or
# you will ship a stale game. See "Deploying" in the README.

